Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:34.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\ngood evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:41.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The youth, who had been ravaged by poison,\nwas restored to life through my friend's efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:44.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, my friend\nsaid something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:47.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let his soul\nbe lost yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:53.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not until the day that he himself\nsnuffs out that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.93,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,350)}Act 10:\NThe Letter From Edmond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:28.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you managed\nto get any sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If there is one thing I have\nconfidence in, it's my stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:55.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you look\nlike hell to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:59.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like all the maids\nhave been laid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:07.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave her alone\nin this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:12.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Franz told\nme something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:17.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage isn't necessarily the only way\nto make the person you love happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I've been mulling it over\nas best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:25.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is the one thing that she\nneeds most of all right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilien...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:32.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She may be asleep now, but I think\nthat Mademoiselle Valentine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:35.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is lonely to the\npoint of crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:42.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I at least want to be by her side\nwhen she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I made up\nmy mind today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:49.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take her to my family home\nin Marseilles to recuperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:53.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want her to have to endure\nany more suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling that\nyou would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your Honor, I came here today\nto discuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mark my words, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:08.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you to try to take my daughter\nso much as one foot out of this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:12.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The instant you do, I'll have you\narrested as a kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is no threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:16.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the things that are happening\nin this house are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are none of\nyour business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:22.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get out! You too, Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:26.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Begging your pardon, sir,\Nbut someone\nis trying to kill your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I myself was almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By "someone," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If there is anyone close to hand\Nwho could be described as suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it would be that impudent\nfraud of a Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:40.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are we clear?! From now on,\nthis is strictly a family matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I strictly forbid you\nfrom interfering!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:52.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The following is a report regarding my\ninvestigation on the Count of Monte Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:57.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the course of visiting the various\nlocations indicated by Your Honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:04.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I discovered by accident that a certain old\npriest was making a similar set of inquiries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:10.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He has visited this area several times\nduring the past three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:17.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The priest seems to be gathering information\non an old man who died penniless here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:22.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The old man's name\nwas Louis Dantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In order to ascertain the\npriest's objectives,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:30.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as well as to clarify the connection\nbetween him and the Count of Monte Cristo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:35.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I plan to investigate the house that\NLouis Dantes lived in while he was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:40.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The old man's name\nwas Louis Dantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dantes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dantes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:51.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, my school play is today.\NYou're coming, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:56.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't your mother tell you? I'm sorry,\nbut some urgent business has come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:01.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you promised! You said that you would\ncome this time, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:05.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Papa's work keeps him\nvery busy, Edouard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:08.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that!\NYou're a liar, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:13.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get him out of here. It's your job as his\nmother to explain these things to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:18.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But Edouard has been so\nexcited about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:21.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how excited he was!\NStop bothering me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:34.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell my teacher that the\Nyellow dwarf\nisn't gonna be in the play!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:48.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here?\NHurry up and get your bags packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:53.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An invitation... An invitation\nto a funeral just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning\nof this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:09.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all well and good that I've\ninherited vast land holdings,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:12.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but there's still so much\nthat I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:16.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing is to learn the law\ninside and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:20.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That goes doubly so when you've come\ninto possession of a huge inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:25.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't keep estate taxes and whatnot\nunder control, it can become a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:34.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Truth be told, I'm looking for a partner who will\nbe able to effectively manage my assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:38.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a partner,\nyou say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:51.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mademoiselle Eugenie, would it be all right if\NI paid you a visit in your room after I'm done?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:54.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm in the middle\nof my piano lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:02.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for Heaven's sake...\NPlease forgive her lack of charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is just between\nyou and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:09.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but there's a bit of a scandal beginning\nto brew around her fiancée's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:20.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:39.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have a letter here\nfor the General.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:40.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond Dantes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,\nare you working?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's all right.\NI was just finishing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:08.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that I want\nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is, eh?\NHave a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:16.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the election is drawing near, there are\na lot of matters that have to be taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:19.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can imagine.\NOh, this was addressed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A funeral invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:32.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, I just got back\nfrom Villefort Manor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to get Valentine\naway from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:41.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if there was anything\nthat you could do to persuade her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:45.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's in great danger\nevery minute she stays there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:49.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If the request came from you,\NMonsieur Villefort might listen to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:54.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you feel the need to poke your\nnose into another family's affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, why?\NMy friend is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:10:01.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Neither you nor your friend have any right\nto throw someone else's house into turmoil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:04.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?! You have\nno idea what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do something,\nshe'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:09.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My answer is no!\NDon't get involved any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you\nso angry about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:14.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My friend is in trouble, and you're\ntelling me to just abandon her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. It was stupid of me\nto even ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:42.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NYou look upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got into a shouting match\nwith Father, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:52.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, do you know someone\nnamed Edmond Dantes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond Dantes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:11:00.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That was the name of the sender\non a letter that came for Father today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:06.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The instant Father saw that name, he started\nacting strangely for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:12.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:17.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. I haven't been\nsleeping well lately, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:22.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With the election race almost here,\NI bet you're tired, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that might\nbe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he? Who's this\N"Edmond Dantes" person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That man is\nlong since dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:10.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What could be worth coming\nall the way out here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:35.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, you were sent\none of these, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:46.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a stupid prank.\NLet's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But they knew us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:51.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Someone knows about the connection\nbetween the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:00.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, the gang's\nall here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell\nare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:21.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your old friend Caderousse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've made it big,\nhave you forgotten about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...along with all those\nunpleasant memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:32.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're all big, powerful men now,\nnot at all like you were in the old days!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:37.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's behind this, Caderousse?\NWhat kind of stupid stunt is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:43.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have one of\nthese invitations, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:52.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else knows\nabout us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:59.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:06.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me who else knows\nbesides the four of us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond Dantes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But he was sent to the\NChateau d'lf and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:19.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I thought\nhe died there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:22.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The dead man has\ncome back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:27.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond would never forget\nwhat we did to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:33.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He would never forget what we did,\nnot in a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whose body is\nin here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is in this coffin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way!\NI don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your whimpering\nand open the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:55.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:44.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boville!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:03.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay for us\nto be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:30.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, did you hear something\nupstairs just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:35.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. Maybe your grandfather\nfell out of his wheelchair again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:39.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And with Valentine asleep, there's\nno one to help him up, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, it might turn out to be\na good rehabilitation exercise for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:48.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Noirtier...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:16.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will keep Mademoiselle Valentine safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it me, or is he saying that\nhe wants us to go that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!\NWas it really her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You sure were gone a long time.\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of\nyour business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:43.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!\NI'm so offended!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:47.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, and here I was gonna give you\nsome great news...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:50.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:53.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilien finally decided\nto put his plan into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:19:00.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The scene of the crime, Villefort Manor.\NAccomplices, two. Franz and Renaud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They came here to get you,\nbut you weren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:41.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! Commander!\NThis is Edouard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:48.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Three criminals spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!\NApprehend them immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:56.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And just what do you think you're doing\nwith my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing\nin here, my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:26.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be doing a lot\nof research regarding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you\nhope to uncover?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:37.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something about me? Or about\nthe Count of Monte Cristo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:42.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to tell you\nabout both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:44.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...far faster this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:04.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:07.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:12.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be some sort of\ncommotion in front of the manor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:13.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:20.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:23.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Summon my men\nat once!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:13.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The lovers depart,\nand new misgivings arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:16.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unexpected news leaves me\nat a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:19.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo act 11:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.53,0:23:21.25,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,350)}Act 11:\NAn Engagement Broken
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:21.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."An Engagement Broken."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:23.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope!
